name: Lil Gy (Pidgey)
description:
Not as useless in battles as they think. Deceives his opponents with a weaker simpler appearance but creates massive gusts of wind that sweep up stones and sand to blind his opponent.

He's a fast flyer and Flys even higher when toking that good stuff if you know what I mean.


Dm for unlockables on purchase. COLLAB WITH agkphotography
